blog.name: fandomshatelgbtqpeople
blog.title: Fandoms Hate LGBTQ+ People
blog.description:
Our purpose at FHQP is to talk about the treatment of the LGBTQ+ community, both in media and in fandom. We aim to tackle fandom fetishization and all forms of hate and discrimination against characters and fans who are LGBTQIAP+. 
We will also post about celebrities who fall under these categories and real world issues we face.

summary: Tmw a YouTuber you liked says that aces shouldn't be part of the LGBT+ community and other aces agree with them. It makes me...
question: Tmw a YouTuber you liked says that aces shouldn't be part of the LGBT+ community and other aces agree with them. It makes me kinda sad, honestly.
answer:
It sucks if there’s ace folks who don’t feel as though they belong to the LGBTQIA+ community- even more sucks if there’s influencers, like youtubers, saying that crap. What youtuber was it, may I ask, so people can be aware? 

Mod S
